- [CircleVideoComposer.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoComposer.tsx): Integrated local progress bars and background-close capability.
- [App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./heart-lens-studio-main/src/App.tsx): Registered the upload provider and global overlay.

- [20260319110000_circle_video_interactions.sql](file:///c:/Users/elink/./heart-lens-studio-main/supabase/migrations/20260319110000_circle_video_interactions.sql): [NEW] Database schema.
